citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
* A facility representative was not available on 1/5/16 at 4:30 PM to do a facility inspection.
* Inspector knocked on the front door of the licensees house. Inspector called telephone numbers given by the
licensee. Per phone conservation, licensee stated that they had a prior commitment and would not be available to
do a facility inspection.
* Copy of inspection report was sent by regular mail.
Additional Inspectors
Shaver Margaret, Veterinary Medical Officer
